# API Jbuilder and OpenAPI

Jbuilder templates define the real JSON contract. When you change `app/views/api/**`, update `specs/api/` (paths/schemas) and run `bundle exec rake openapi:validate`. See rule `api-openapi` for layout and versioning (`/api` vs `/api/v1`).
